PRO EDITION

A commercial Pro Edition with additional features, setup services, and
ongoing support is available separately. The Pro Edition includes:

  - Direct POS integrations (Square, Shopify, Clover, Lightspeed)
  - Advanced analytics (weekday benchmarking, anomaly detection,
    seasonality, forecasting)
  - Context-aware human-readable insights
  - Custom branding (logos, color themes)
  - Multi-business / multi-location support
  - Rich HTML email with insights summary
  - SMS, WhatsApp, and Slack delivery channels
  - Setup, deployment, and ongoing support

